Oh&#8230; oh&#8230;</p>
<p>We were kids, some of us grew up<br />
The others haven&#8217;t, they remained angels<br />
You hold the key, the door is closed<br />
Behind them lives an angel with wings</p>
<p>You&#8217;re an angel, don’t you believe?<br />
An angel predicted your way<br />
You&#8217;re an angel, did you forget?<br />
Your love proves it</p>
<p>Oh&#8230; oh&#8230;<br />
